## Description {#details}

Serializable representation of stack object from the <a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/yaml/machineframeinfo">MachineFrameInfo</a> class.

The flags &#39;isImmutable&#39; and &#39;isAliased&#39; aren&#39;t serialized, as they are determined by the object&#39;s type and frame information flags. Dead stack objects aren&#39;t serialized.

The &#39;isPreallocated&#39; flag is determined by the local offset.

Definition at line 245 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/codegen/miryamlmapping-h">MIRYamlMapping.h</a>.
